    <p>Theme: Love This Christ­mas</p>
    <p>Light-up pe­riod: From Nov 13 un­til Jan 1</p>
    <p>Time of light-up:</p>
    <p>6.30pm to mid­night (Sun­days to Thurs­days) 6.30pm to 2am (Fri­days and Satur­days)</p>
    <p>6.30pm to 6am (Christ­mas Eve and New Year’s Eve)</p>
    <p>Or­gan­iser: Or­chard Road Busi­ness As­so­ci­a­tion</p>
    <p>To­tal length of LED string lights: About 50km</p>
    <p>To­tal length of Christ­mas light-up: 2.9km</p>
    <p>Height of main arch: 14m</p>
    <p>Num­ber of lamp posts dec­o­rated with lights: 171</p>
    <p>To­tal man hours spent putting up Christ­mas dec­o­ra­tions in Or­chard Road: 10,300</p>


